other_tests.findings: Within the right lower quadrant, there is a 2 x 2 cm fluid and air containing structure with surrounding mild haziness/stranding concerning for phlegmon in a periappendiceal region. The terminal ileum is unremarkable. Hypodense structures most likely representing cysts are seen in the bilateral ovaries, measuring 2.4 cm on the right and 2.3 cm on the left.
